# Components

## Self-contained

Each component file owns its markup, local state, and colocated types. Accept data via props; emit via callbacks. Parent handles server calls.

## Reuse hierarchy

1. Existing `app/components/*` (e.g. `PasswordInput`, `PlatformIcon`, `DebouncedFieldErrors`)
2. Compose smaller local subcomponents in `app/components/{feature}/`
3. New shared primitive only when used in 2+ features

## Do not duplicate

- Field errors → `DebouncedFieldErrors`
- Password fields → `PasswordInput`
- Platform icons → `PlatformIcon`
- Layout chrome → `AppLayout`
- AI setup UI → `AiWorkspace`

## File structure (feature folder)

```
app/components/connect-channels/
  connect-channels-modal.tsx   # primary export
  channel-tile.tsx
  connected-channel-card.tsx
  index.ts                     # barrel re-export (optional)
```

## Size

Split when a file exceeds ~200 lines or mixes unrelated concerns (e.g. modal + form + guide in one file).
